# Implementation Plan - Sprint 4: Messaging Module

This plan outlines the implementation of the Messaging module, focusing on real-time communication between patients (via WhatsApp) and clinic staff (via the dashboard).

## User Review Required

> [!IMPORTANT]
> The WhatsApp integration currently lacks a real Business API connection. For now, we will use a webhook simulation for inbound messages and a simulated response for outbound messages. Real integration will follow once n8n or a direct API is connected.

